org.sdm.spa.actors.transport

Class FileCopierBase.CopyResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sdm.spa.actors.transport.FileCopierBase.CopyResult
  • Enclosing class:
    FileCopierBase

    public class FileCopierBase.CopyResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Object that contains the exit code and (error) message associated with the copy operation. Expects a exit code of 0 to denote successful file transfer. If exit code is zero, the error message is set to empty string
